  "texts": [
    "This metric is a variation on a learned evaluation BLEU score, called the Bilingual Evaluation Understudy with Representations from Transformers (BLEURT).",
    "BLEURT was a regression-based metric that was fine-tuned on clinical notes [14].",
    "Methods Problem Summarization Shared Task for Diagnosis GenerationWe utilized data from the Problem List BioNLP Summarization (ProbSum) 2023 Shared Task [1], which was one of the first natural language generation tasks in the medical domain.",
    "The goal of this task was to summarize a patient's active problems/diagnoses given the Subjective, Objective, and Assessment sections from the daily progress notes.",
    "The Plan section was used to label the gold standard diagnoses."
  ],
